(Steps:) Tj
0 -12 Td
(1. Build & flash firmware to Arduino Nano 33 BLE \(use Arduino IDE\).) Tj
0 -12 Td
(2. Run collector locally and label while playing:) Tj
0 -12 Td
(    python collector/collect_data.py) Tj
0 -12 Td
(3. After collecting enough labeled rows, train:) Tj
0 -12 Td
(    python train/train_bat_model.py) Tj
0 -12 Td
(4. Run dashboard locally with hardware:) Tj
0 -12 Td
(    python dashboard/smart_bat_dashboard.py --ble) Tj
0 -12 Td
(   Or simulate:) Tj
0 -12 Td
(    python dashboard/smart_bat_dashboard.py --test) Tj
0 -12 Td
(5. Replay recorded CSV:) Tj
0 -12 Td
(    python dashboard/replay_dashboard.py data_collection/training_data.csv) Tj
0 -12 Td
() Tj
